metadata.name: Cubist Anatolia
metadata.description:
A folk poet on Anatolian rug motifs with a saz in his hand... A synthesis of rug weaving and minstrel tradition, which Anatolian Turks have been continuing since the time they lived in Central Asia, with the possibilities of modern art...
       This photograph was created by collaging the photographs taken with a digital camera in a computer environment with a cubist approach.

1993x2739
